Author: Gateway#3763
Content:
[telegram] <gcharang> @Omboti
the base nodes are enough to launch your Smart Chain and be ready to grow the network
but they might not be able to tolerate the load of a lot of new nodes connecting to them at the same time
so, if you are expecting a sudden influx of new nodes (as it happens during a Public launch), adding additional nodes (2 to 3) is a good idea
once other nodes are started and become part of the network, the load on the nodes maintained by the Antara Composer should decrease significantly
you can find help from the team directly in the #antara-composer-beta channel of our discord server: https://komodoplatform.com/discord
